SUM(number1, [number2], ...)
Adds all the numbers in a range of cells
=SUM(A1:A3)
number1
number1,number2,... are 1 to 255 numbers to sum. Logical values and text are ignored in cells, included if typed as arguments
[number2]
number1,number2,... are 1 to 255 numbers to sum. Logical values and text are ignored in cells, included if typed as arguments
